Package: devil
Title: devil
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person("Giovanni", "Santacatterina", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="santacatterinagiovanni@gmail.com"))
Description: devil is an R package for fast and scalable single-cell differential expression analysis using sandwich covariance estimators to account for multi-patient variability, with optional GPU acceleration for efficient inference.
